<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row p-4 pb-0 pe-lg-0 pt-lg-5 align-items-center rounded-3 border shadow-lg">
        <div class="col-lg-7 p-3 p-lg-5 pt-lg-3">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold lh-1">@ViewData["BoxTitle"]</h1>
            <p class="lead">@ViewData["BoxDescription"]</p>
            <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start mb-4 mb-lg-3">
                <a type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-md-2 fw-bold" asp-area="" asp-controller="Calendar" asp-action="Secret">
                    Get Started
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 offset-lg-1 p-0 overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img class="rounded-lg-3" src="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/examples/heroes/bootstrap-docs.png" alt="" width="720">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3 align-items-center rounded-3 border shadow-lg">
        <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#calendar3"></use></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2>Make plans</h2>
                <p>Plan your future events with us. There are a lot of features that you can use. Thanks for choosing our app!</p>
                <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Calendar" asp-action="Secret" class="btn btn-primary">
                    Try making plans
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#geo-fill"></use></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2>Choose location</h2>
                <p>When you add new event in our app you can choose location of this event and then see.</p>
                <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Calendar" asp-action="Secret" class="btn btn-primary">
                    Try choosing location
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark flex-shrink-0 me-3">
                <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#home"></use></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2>See weather forecast</h2>
                <p>In our app you can see weather forecast in the location of your planned event. Also you can see actual weather forecast.</p>
                <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Calendar" asp-action="Secret" class="btn btn-primary">
                    Try seeing forecast
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>